<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Listing Rejected — AddressGuru</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swapping" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #fdf2f2; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #333; }
    .wrapper { width: 100%; padding: 40px 0; background: #fdf2f2; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; background: #fff; margin: auto; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9e35, #ffb347); text-align: center; padding: 30px 20px; color: #ffffff; }
    .header img { width: 150px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .header h1 { font-size: 22px; margin: 0; font-weight: 600; }
    .content { padding: 30px 25px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .content p { margin: 15px 0; }
    .reason-box {
      background: #fee2e2;
      border: 1px solid #fca5a5;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      color: #b91c1c;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .footer { background: #fafafa; padding: 25px 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #777; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    .footer a { color: #f7941d; text-decoration: none; }
    .footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .content { padding: 20px 15px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <a href="https://addressguru.ae" target="_blank">
          <img src="https://www.addressguru.in/images/logopng.png" alt="AddressGuru Logo">
        </a>
        <h1>Listing Rejected</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>
          We reviewed your listing <strong>“{{listingTitle}}”</strong>, but unfortunately it was not approved for the following reason:
        </p>
        <div class="reason-box">
          {{rejectionReason}}
        </div>
        <p>
          You may correct the issue(s) and resubmit your listing for review. If you need help, feel free to contact support.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} AddressGuru. All rights reserved. <br>
        <a href="https://addressguru.ae" target="_blank">addressguru.ae</a> | <a href="mailto:support@addressguru.ae">support@addressguru.ae</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
